{"tid":1841463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Repost] 區議員可唔可以考慮代購口罩","createTime":"2020-01-25T09:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T14:58:45.000Z","uid":236171,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4b3059169eb4509222d65fe5d53121feaf09de78","tid":1841463,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:24:25.000Z","msg":"見到唔少區議員開始派口罩<br />\n但明白區議會未必有資金買大量口罩免費派<br />\n行動未必可持續，而且派都係每人一兩個<br />\n咁樣長遠幫助有限<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係如果幫手代購有冇得諗呢？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我哋後生嘅上網買就冇乜問題<br />\n但係好多公公婆婆唔識買<br />\n佢地喺香港搵唔到口罩<br />\n就算搵到都要捱貴口罩、買錯支那假貨<br />\n甚至有啲因此決定唔戴<br />\n<br />\n如果區議會幫手代購/同集運商合作幫居民買口罩，可唔可行呢？<br />\n<br />\n居民去辦事處/街站用成本價落單，留低電話。區議員 by batch 訂貨，口罩到貨可以落去攞。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲都係地區工作嘅一部分，唔好忽略。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b0db8e2459f158fb0b3e7255b74b9a56dadd78","tid":1841463,"uid":236171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"如果代購嘅話區議員只需要支出 Logistics 費用<br />\n必要時甚至可以加收手續費以達致收支平衡<br />\n<br />\n咁樣應該可以持續性地提供都口罩俾香港人<br />\n啲錢又可以用嚟做其他有意義嘅地區工作"},{"pid":"2ebef552e09bb6a0399e690c742739737cb59559","tid":1841463,"uid":293539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:27:31.000Z","msg":"眼入呀 係要買泳鏡"},{"pid":"d76f968821cc9e5f3fec5cd21aeabd141931c5fd","tid":1841463,"uid":25771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"區議員就黎邊百寶袋"},{"pid":"85c0f971bed9fa1eda065819581484e7e715c189","tid":1841463,"uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ebef552e09bb6a0399e690c742739737cb59559","tid":1841463,"uid":293539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:27:31.000Z","msg":"眼入呀 係要買泳鏡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:29:45.000Z","msg":"有需要可以加埋其他衛生用品落代購清單<br />\n包括消毒藥水、漂白水、酒精搓手液"},{"pid":"ce7316972a0ad8eb0113a675ba55d769ce0f619e","tid":1841463,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"PISH!"},{"pid":"242f56d0359ff48b4c8312f480c1ad5280ca84b8","tid":1841463,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf5d0a075d52172353d4a91a9bd68faa2ab0cf8","tid":1841463,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9053673cdd8e6117f82eb763bf9f05d01189ea","tid":1841463,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94f072b0d29a0791ee5982029bd187bb84db2c1","tid":1841463,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:33:58.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"e5e293bf563feb9df9061932e2ef0b3432d98eb8","tid":1841463,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0754fa239a4aac5a4d13bc06080cc3c21a9f347","tid":1841463,"uid":151022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:35:23.000Z","msg":"我果區d區議員好早就開團購啦，只係貨唔夠派"},{"pid":"c46d29c24a838f693a022114a50ddc63a2bd6d0f","tid":1841463,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:35:39.000Z","msg":"推到區議員見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c9b1dcbfd186b4a44fdb3bee0c28c6fbe83c69","tid":1841463,"uid":